data.description: This beautiful property is located in the city of Tavares, with exclusive access to Lake Dora. Lake Dora is a freshwater lake located in Central Florida, It is part of the Harris Chain of Lakes, which includes several interconnected lakes. Lake Dora is known for its scenic beauty, boating opportunities, and recreational activities. This house on Lake Dora, in Tavares Florida is a spacious and luxurious property with three bedrooms, three bathrooms, The interior of the house is designed with an open-concept layout, the living, dining, and kitchen areas were designed with a keen sense for family time. Large windows throughout the house provide plenty of natural light and offer stunning views of the pool, the surrounding landscape and Lake Dora.The kitchen is equipped with high-end appliances, granite countertops, and unique patterns in the design. The house is situated on a large piece of land, providing ample privacy and space for various outdoor activities. A beautiful patio area, perfect for outdoor dining, relaxation, and entertainment, stretches across the back of the house. The property boasts acres of land that lead down to the pristine shores of Lake Dora, making it an ideal waterfront property. The property has a large garage for several vehicles. It also has another 2 Bay fixture that is for storing anything you heart desires. It is apart from the house and has a connection for an RV motor home. The home is close to downtown where fine dining and entertainment awaits. This home was completely Renovated and is an oasis for a family that loves the water life, Complete with a boat slip and Dock. This home is a must see.
